    "text": "Đặt $G(2014+t) = S(t) = 90,7e^{0,014t} + C$; $G(2014+0) = 90,7 \\Rightarrow 90,7e^{0,014 \\cdot 0} + C = 90,7 \\Rightarrow C = 0$\n$\\Rightarrow S(t) = 90,7e^{0,014t}$."
  },
